p: We test three different versions of this model to qualitatively compare the model behaviour with different factors included. In phase 0, each of the parameters are taken from table 1, and the model behaviour serves as a baseline. Phase 1 tests the behavioural model in equation (2.2) in isolation, with q = 1.0. Phase 2 varies both η and q as given by equations (2.2) and (2.10), respectively.
